  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK236">
<l>tōṉṟiṟ pukaḻōṭu tōṉṟuka vaḵtilār</l>
<l>tōṉṟaliṟ ṟōṉṟāmai naṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you are born (in this world), be born with qualities conductive to fame. From those who are destitute of them it will be better not to be born.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
